  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>패키지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0757ca03-6029-4d59-9c9c-c30cca2358c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-edaf163b-6e66-42bf-8bfb-5d0ee0f42124\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>소량 생산업체</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>공장직영 맞춤 제작</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5dc28254-abcd-44d7-8714-d5fcead9b113\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 전문</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e82de4f-9a69-4e27-a67c-68522040907a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4101916d-9615-4780-8684-4e967e96a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-156e84ba-4ae8-4562-ac8a-0b0c2d8c4089\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81bb8efa-d230-4ee9-ad8d-dc33e90d7d5d\" style=\"\">단상자가 A3 안에 들어간다면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4a517379-6f78-4d94-bbed-54412ba82167\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-359d4892-16be-4c35-a2f0-7bab0af91df5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0b6e608f-8d03-40d1-987d-1afd988a31fd\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>소량 생산에서 가장 중요한 것은 사이즈입니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2923c20-65e3-4678-8a5c-f7ff449420ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 일단 사이즈가 디지털 인쇄에 적합하지 않다면 빠른 출고가 불가능해집니다. 물론 전혀 불가능한 것은 아니지만 생각하시는 급한 시간만큼 납품하는 것은 어려울 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d5fc5e3-2242-46a5-932e-5eca74bb48b7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-397fe280-755d-4783-840d-1c25c03f14e5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ae1aeec7-e524-48e7-8bba-51e259b866e6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d480a42-26e6-4d31-82ba-58ada561597a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 이유로 거의 모든 문의하시는 분들이 가능 여부만 여쭤보시고 정작 중요한 부분의 정보를 주시지는 않으십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b5468c8-a6de-4fd6-92c6-1fe2cc60bdbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d56bfdb9-2302-497a-9a9c-368284fdb4a5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcd8a83d-5423-4322-b2c8-f8e85683cc6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1d3c40da-80ed-48ee-bad1-dc08a4e2ab92\" style=\"color:#555555;\">빠른 납기를 함께 만들기 위해 다음의 정보는 반드시 말해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-73e287cb-09d1-45ed-a46f-d0dd6d5ff433\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aff64e23-5b35-4cb9-9b54-4c3bd72c295a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8963c350-d0ac-4e4b-9c11-293fb1a8e9ba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-81cc3118-c080-4545-a468-f4cdeaaac914\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-42b9bd9d-e8f6-4d44-8b49-8adb03c21bc7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2534fe0-2b42-4dd2-b185-eda11408f0c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈는 가장 중요합니다. 우리가 흔히 아는 일반적인 A3 사이즈 안에 들어가는 단상자라면 빠른 출고가 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80b5f162-0d70-4cb6-b2fb-139ba4a35440\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:685px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-464070e4-60b5-4016-bcf0-3ebe49c6dcd8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e4de821-4729-4c0d-b5e2-eda7741c641d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6fd6a41e-4fcb-477b-a0f6-01e8b5b23625\" style=\"color:#555555;\">장/폭/고를 일단 알면 펼친 면 사이즈를 파악할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-168d6001-8bd0-43b5-b568-764db33f3f70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b859981d-2e43-434a-8f04-7fc8ff963b87\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f3178ae9-a24f-4a85-89eb-4e753118a11f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d79571a6-4d50-457e-ae51-f296ecb8c93d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트로 이동하셔서 패키지 칼선을 무료로 다운로드해서 펼친 면 사이즈를 파악해 보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a592a28-e893-454c-8ec7-001832b2937f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92e58d1e-bc4e-4f9b-8a1b-046ac2a5f8d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://cookthedesign.co.kr/product/pg_singlebox.html?cs=014002001\" target=\"_blank\">https://(주)파파스컴퍼니.co.kr/product/pg_singlebox.html?cs=014002001</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8a6f6843-a4f7-42d5-852b-500e86cb0aa6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cd73ea97-ffaf-4a3b-9ce8-631e5de91f5a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-095d1755-00ed-4c53-9597-3a86bc3b1b7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그 펼친 면 전체 사이즈가 A3 안에 들어가면 일단 출고를 빠르게 진행하는 조건이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3e89280-3887-4a0a-bd33-daf40a19935c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d20d369e-d65e-4fcd-a0bd-a613b4784a98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e195fd65-ae59-434c-ba33-091ce28663ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ece9ca6d-b6ed-482c-8ac9-20c11cf09045\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 이 이야기는 단상자에 한하여 진행됩니다. 싸바리 박스나 합지 박스는 당일 또는 익일 출고가 어렵습니다. 하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 급한 고객의 시간을 위해 싸바리 박스도 2~4일 안에 출고하는 샘플 시스템을 구축 중에 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d10a732-bd87-4d24-a0aa-7717a901470b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0d67f27-45e6-4424-a892-b7f4cc9feacc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4d2ec02a-e687-45d1-b5f0-f87965e43a59\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-69d584ad-2550-4374-b424-6d7508b18789\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음은 오늘 들어온 문의 스샷입니다. 여기 대화에서 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-264b5b64-16d5-4921-a8dc-238284616646\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>가장 중요한 것은</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7fdbedcd-3b0d-4444-b77e-b2ee2a0cc573\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b> 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3239133-fb2a-4da5-9cdc-2155e96d1050\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7740138-1c0e-4aab-bd21-22ad093d78ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65234594-b233-46a9-b5e8-6fd1d3201081\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8b0b7393-8494-428c-8d8d-45d9ca7a4910\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:435px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-947ce2db-88a1-4d4b-aed2-ee7715c710c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8520d929-4fc7-4089-b14e-c03dd2ca5b93\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7ab96a55-6dab-4e5c-ba4a-02b612f2c03c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">저희는 먼저 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7725252b-32c6-46a7-921e-0889ab6bd1ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈부터 확인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ebb319da-6753-45df-abf8-f3534790e428\" style=\"color:#555555;\">합니다. 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a9505c9d-3e3a-4b8f-9aed-69a478a7585a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87a2eab1-c94b-455e-906f-3057cf46b6b6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-88d5115c-1b03-4f2b-b3b3-12fdd4beb985\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-97e86bd4-c5fa-42c5-a319-a062d585ef60\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1ba60db4-95c7-48b0-b8f5-d3a7171850cc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0af9c8ba-e31d-4030-9b9b-a979c82e32ec\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음은 디지털에서 가능한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eae5174d-467c-4d82-bee6-60fb341a953c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23362cc5-d6dd-451e-b426-9cc5de6507ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69e0c884-c7b2-4ed7-83f6-7f6f14995685\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2c34afa3-9b56-47e5-8e57-46262354b605\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보통은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e56aae15-1cfb-41e3-b30a-f85223d9ca70\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>패키지용 종이의 평량은 300g ~ 350g 사이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b979001-cf16-4bb4-8ce4-50b2b5755fe7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 물론 일반적인 오프셋의 경우 400g이나 450g도 진행하지만 이 평량은 디지털 인쇄에서는 거의 가능하지 않습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c96f3bde-7093-407b-b10b-c7ee4007b0d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b5cd2240-d540-40fc-a5bf-8c4542628734\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90023d09-9f7a-4d9c-a522-e9a72297e116\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-549f6b5a-58bf-4ce2-abbb-d9463266e47a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슈퍼파인 울트라화이트 324g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-92b548ae-7d92-4215-9856-ed9757647a1b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7a35d40-f4e3-4c1c-8b8f-a36297108f5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">올드밀 화이트 300g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c5d8026-8697-40de-a6c4-ff8a261d5d6e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3fc36274-4f72-405c-b714-1f7e1a8c3058\" style=\"color:#555555;\">센토 엑스트라화이트 350g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7c5feb0-514a-41b9-94b9-7561fdedb006\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-38d6e8e0-16e8-4713-b27b-58659d21053c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인바이런먼트 352g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35a466e5-4752-4848-a75c-29318a62b564\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a33dedf1-e1e5-439a-9f7a-ddcebae40002\" style=\"color:#555555;\">스노우/아트지 300g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6be20286-34d3-4a8c-9d12-7237ed470adf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f33b6dab-1dde-472c-811d-df4f6fe4da32\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0b2e52e9-1305-493e-8888-e87e11ccb7ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b964b37-ffa0-4102-b7af-16a8384f059f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">시리오 펄 스노우 300g(펄지)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c40558ea-4ba7-4f2e-9fd5-85949e03c2a2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ba4e9c62-f153-4ae6-bc4b-dd7579b31d88\" style=\"color:#555555;\">마제스틱 250g(펄지)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b228fb6-4496-4f08-9a0b-93682bb1b17a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f6a906ef-1a1e-4a72-9d4c-cc1ab0e49f67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a416b75f-bbce-4795-8738-16cf8ab63c27\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-65b2a98e-bf25-4881-b76a-954d06745f5e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대부분 백색입니다만 거의 미색의 느낌인 종이도 많습니다. 백상지와 대보면 흰색의 차이는 확연하게 느껴집니다. 하지만 그렇다고 누런 색상들의 종이는 아닙니다. 백색 코팅 과정에서의 차이라고 이해해 주시면 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-14b58b81-1024-45f4-9ea8-515308a44021\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-86cd2f8a-10c7-473f-b633-89d135c0ed2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f323c8e2-f0ec-4a1d-a50e-fcdb7429afa6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e104336b-0f4b-48c7-a8b9-d5ce2553076a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅 유무</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b097d5fb-029f-4fc9-b635-c1888735e394\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7373e3c7-b35a-40ce-a752-4fa7d3d1663c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음은 후공정입니다. 코팅은 기본적으로 하시는 것을 추천드립니다. 가끔 친환경 부분으로 코팅을 생략하기를 원하시는 고객님이 계십니다. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c7f88fe-b1e9-4d2c-b8b0-bc8c33824627\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">하지만 소량에서의 디지털 커팅은 도무송같이 작업되지는 않습니다. 반드시 코팅해서 터집을 방지하시는 것이 좋습니다. 일반 본 작업의 경우 기계로 접고 잡착을 하다 보니 터짐이 덜 할 수도 있지만 (기계 코팅이라도 합니다.) 디지털은 거의 대부분 수작업이므로 터짐이 100% 발생됩니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86b82caf-0ced-4a65-9b53-3f5c9ffbd18b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 반드시 코팅을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37264d59-1fac-4778-a783-68c6d1185625\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-756c0342-4266-4523-9382-260d27e5b526\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-736ea055-a48b-4f54-82f4-0dcd2b40f3b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5faf3380-8c16-4f5b-b252-304267c65909\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1f1f931-c5ca-4c58-9097-fb11e311d143\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e941b407-d10e-407a-b784-26a539d12dbc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">무코팅 터짐 현상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-254267ff-ecb4-4267-92bf-654f7ae7f77c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24eb2da9-6b19-4505-ad1e-776f676dc84b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e389ccdc-a829-445b-8f6e-566bdfec8531\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:561px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f2c8e069-259b-4671-b4ce-664696297094\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0349c4c0-85bd-4353-9c4a-bbdcd9806700\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1e6cd3d8-b170-4282-b3dd-16cad20090cf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">유광 코팅 효과</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0877df94-3784-42f6-b5f0-db22a3bc7c7b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3e129511-9635-4a7d-81c6-ab19c70a0352\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-269388b7-1474-455f-8b6e-a2423a3f93cc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9c0bfcb6-51e2-44ac-9771-cc1e15390540\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>접착 유무</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f077bf85-0b72-42b0-96c0-89b06998bfeb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8727929c-2e35-4fb8-ac74-2b19424abddd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 소량 샘플 작업은 100% 양면테이프로 수작업 진행됩니다. 수량이라 건으로 작업하기도 어렵고 또는 기계를 넣어 자동 접착할 수도 없습니다. 200개 정도까지는 100% 수작업 비용이 청구됩니다. 능숙한 숙련공이라고 하더라도 시간이 다소 걸리고 또한 작업 결과물도 기계 접착보다는 떨어지는 것이 사실입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c0f80e8-44fc-4b67-8f27-4f1f0311273b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5dfd217-5f61-46fc-aa03-4a32158a0939\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-811999a2-69e2-4a58-93e3-abad0ca59dd6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d9aebaa-8440-4373-8292-f6b194fe36c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 정성을 다해 수작업 양면 테이핑을 작업하여 배송해 드리고 있습니다. 다만 납기 시간은 사전 협의가 원칙입니다. 보통은 1~2일 정도 수량에 따라 더 소요됩니다. 참고해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be69e3f1-9994-4078-9508-64b81605d84c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ff6f169-d01e-4c90-a57b-01f41f7c6bae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-466be121-b005-41ed-a408-272a46b3eed6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b5467395-e6e1-41d8-9c95-114c6f0316b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 테이핑 방법도 한면 접착이냐 삼면접착이냐 또는 별도 접착부분이 있는 냐에 따라 달라집니다. 그리고 접착도 테이핑만 하고 고객님이 띠어서 조립할 수도 있습니다. 사전에 협의 드립니다. 고객의 편리성을 고려하여 납품해 드립니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f193f458-8ad3-4fd1-9678-fd2b6df578f8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cd87dad4-d241-45e2-9624-4d76dbde1588\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-152e9eb5-acd1-48fd-ad03-b7f0d01d8a29\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-935267e4-bd59-44f8-b762-efa5a99ac327\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음은 후공정입니다. 코팅은 기본적으로 하시는 것을 추천드립니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-22ea384b-9c9e-4ad0-978e-f7a84e34d374\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a8db0f9f-ae9d-4f25-98e5-c506ce4d6fa8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3f2168e0-24ed-4588-b60a-5e4e30a6ea54\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d8334690-9e83-414b-82c6-3c17234523b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 커팅</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-91be5f41-7e24-4588-bd73-d075ec463fd8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c66d54f-4fe1-4d8c-b627-21601d5bc574\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 커팅에서 가장 문제는 칼이 들리는 이격의 부분입니다. 이 부분은 뭐라고 설명드리기 어려운 부분입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-48701784-9867-4cb6-a405-a0fa88c9181c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b8f8665d-3848-431c-b70b-5e64975ff2a7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0066b96b-460d-4cc5-b72f-7ed1e36aea04\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9dfee8e4-2d14-403a-bea8-44bafa1afc67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 디자인 데이터를 보고 잘 판단해서 가장 잘 처리할 수 있는 부분은 점검합니다. 하지만 저희도 특성상 어쩔 수 없는 부분이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a53fa88-a3a2-4598-9c61-f4750dcad655\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-341e8ecb-9b08-417a-9ba5-8bf8ef8d8398\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e5200d4a-c335-4228-a8ad-2f356326ae82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:694px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c1028d9-ce4a-4228-b00f-98a5e6439132\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:691px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223802567380/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8b63ef90-0b8b-4212-8d41-c7133e28b186\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8b38d81-3cdf-4a07-be8c-18a788c1f168\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ffab650e-ce29-481c-acf8-2f953c7d63b4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 그림의 보충 설명을 하자면 칼들의 이격이 붙어 있어 디지털 칼날이 지나갈 때 잘 뚫리지 않는 현상들이 발생됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c39e833-46c4-4741-885c-ccdd53258f0e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9900385-e6bf-4784-9d42-51c190d0afb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-841adba1-3cd1-44dd-b9c1-9f2d956b832e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa75f40a-a220-42ba-9124-0aea13543485\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\"><b>디지털 커팅은 아직 톰슨처럼 정교하거나 완벽하지 않습니다. 이 점은 분명합니다. 반드시 샘플용으로 제작하셔야 함을 명심해 주십시오.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eafa17c5-f54f-4008-96ad-a8aba506e5c4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7a43ab9b-9ba6-40f2-a944-44e4c068f24d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbb4bad1-de90-4f27-ba19-06be3c078ee6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0dbe1a12-7488-4422-8216-47ca3f786266\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 최선을 다해 고객의 마음으로 제작해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af0e24de-8f65-4676-b469-116224911098\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5a97b4a0-2afb-43c3-83ba-d41d53f596dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08de88dd-9501-41ec-8e81-367f939e4738\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-139c889d-45a7-4ef6-8360-494ac4890ed2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>항상 고객의 성공을 기원드리며 함께 성장하는 회사가 되겠습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223802567380#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}